{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-134","title":"道德品质","sectionId":"chapter-06","sectionTitle":"人体奥秘知多少","pageStart":678,"pageEnd":681,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":14,"duplicateEntryCount":18,"pages":[{"number":678,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"134 道德品质"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"moral [ˈmɒrəl]","headword":"moral"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.道德的n.道德"},{"type":"entry","text":"social morality 社会公德","headword":"social morality"},{"type":"entry","text":"code of conduct 行为准则","headword":"code of conduct"},{"type":"entry","text":"valour [ˈvælə(r)]","headword":"valour"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.英勇，勇猛"}]},{"number":679,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"courtesy card优待卡，优惠卡","headword":"courtesy card"},{"type":"entry","text":"sharp mind 头脑敏锐","headword":"sharp mind"},{"type":"entry","text":"grace [ɡreɪs]","headword":"grace"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.恩惠"}]},{"number":680,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"take responsibility负责任","headword":"take responsibility"},{"type":"entry","text":"virtue ethics德行伦理学","headword":"virtue ethics"},{"type":"entry","text":"moral example 道德榜样","headword":"moral example"},{"type":"entry","text":"civic virtue 公民道德","headword":"civic virtue"}]},{"number":681,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"public opinion 社会舆论","headword":"public opinion"},{"type":"entry","text":"traditional custom 传统习俗","headword":"traditional custom"},{"type":"entry","text":"inner belief 内心信念","headword":"inner belief"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Will you pick me up from the airport?（你能去机场接我吗？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Of course. It is a courtesy to our guests.（当然。这是我们为客"},{"type":"text","text":"人提供的一项免费服务。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：I can't believe he had a huge party while his parents were gone."},{"type":"text","text":"（难以置信他在父母不在的时候办了这么大